ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains lab tests commonly used for a Bicarbonate lab test from an arterial blood specimen source.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who had a Bicarbonate lab test on a specimen source of arterial blood. Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element would map to 'Laboratory Test, performed'.),(Inclusion Criteria: Bicarbonate lab test using the specimen source of arterial blood.),(Exclusion Criteria: Bicarbonate lab test using a specimen source of Blood other than arterial (ex. venous or capillary).)
